headline: Agilent Unveils Transformative Seahorse XF Flex Analyzer: Revolutionizing 3D Tissue and Organoid Research
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., May 01, 2025--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced release of the new Seahorse XF Flex Analyzer, a high-performance, 24-well system designed to expand real-time metabolic analysis into optimized 3D tissue and organoid workflows, along with dedicated consumables and kit.
